channel.title: Compiler Issue
channel.description:
Okay so my server and client all run great, I guess it was precompiled? (Basically, I didn't need to compile on download to run it successfully). I wasn't concerned with it at first, as a lot of stuff like drops, I can change without compiliing, however, now I'm trying to get deeper and modify some of the more complex areas in the coding, but I get an error with the compiler:
"Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details."
Can anyone tell me what this means or what I should do? Sorry, I'm pretty new to all of this.
